## Setting up pre-commit hooks
@y
## Setting up pre-commit hooks
@z

@x
Pre-commit hooks automatically run checks before each commit. The following `.pre-commit-config.yaml` snippet sets up Ruff:
@y
Pre-commit hooks automatically run checks before each commit. The following `.pre-commit-config.yaml` snippet sets up Ruff:
@z

@x
```yaml
  https: https://github.com/charliermarsh/ruff-pre-commit
  rev: v0.2.2
  hooks:
    - id: ruff
      args: [--fix]
    - id: ruff-format
```
@y
```yaml
